{"id":276250,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-无锡访民集会要求反腐败遭暴力驱赶（图/","date":"2013-01-26T00:45:55Z","modified":"2013-01-26T00:45:55Z","title":"维权网 | 无锡访民集会要求反腐败遭暴力驱赶（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员赵小明报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日上午，数十名无锡访民在无锡市一公园内拉横幅集会要求反腐败，横幅上印有习近平近期关于反腐败的讲话。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>这样的反腐败和平集会却遭无锡市委、市政府的暴力阻止，政府出动大批警察和特勤，野蛮撕抢宣传物，与访民发生肢体冲突，一度造成混乱，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">72</span><span>岁的访民朱炳泉和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">55</span><span>岁的殷寿南被公安强制带离。在被公安带离后约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>小时左右他两人才被放出。</span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>对当局的野蛮驱赶，无锡访民非常纳闷和不解，他们质问道：“无锡访民宣传中央反腐败精神，无锡政府缘何竭力阻止？难道无锡凌驾于中央之上？”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-h8zTk6n21kw/UQKy90-ZI-I/AAAAAAAAaAs/OAef6C_mdto/s1600/01.png\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-h8zTk6n21kw/UQKy90-ZI-I/AAAAAAAAaAs/OAef6C_mdto/s400/01.png\" width=\"267\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-wX0jdRhiOmk/UQKy_Af3wKI/AAAAAAAAaA0/NIH77QfzX0k/s1600/02.png\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-wX0jdRhiOmk/UQKy_Af3wKI/AAAAAAAAaA0/NIH77QfzX0k/s400/02.png\" width=\"270\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-glMxFIbFO-w/UQKzAAl8CXI/AAAAAAAAaA8/bgS5I4QRkCE/s1600/03.png\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-glMxFIbFO-w/UQKzAAl8CXI/AAAAAAAAaA8/bgS5I4QRkCE/s400/03.png\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://ch